name: The Fight
description:
The fight between good & evil.

What defines our perception of good & evil. Our perspectives of the world are as diverse as those of us who walk upon it. Our upbringing, socio-economic status, education and life experiences etc, skew the way we see the world. Who or what we like and dislike. Who we love and who we hate. 

Our reality differs from those around us, but we are all just living inside a mass delusion built on ego and emotions.

Multi-layered collage by @dehiscenceart, 2021.
